== Aho biherereye ==
Urugomero rwa [[Rusizi]] IV rw ' amashanyarazi ruherereye  ku mugezi wa Ruzizi, unyura ku mupaka uhuriweho cg ( uhana imbibi)  n’u [[Rwanda]] na [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]] (DC). Aho iherereye ni 5 kilometres (3 mi), , iburengerazuba bw 'umujyi wa Bugarama, mu [[Akarere ka Rusizi|Karere ka Rusizi]], mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|Ntara y’Uburengerazuba]], 252 kilometres (157 mi), mu majyepfo y'uburengerazuba bwa [[Kigali]], umurwa mukuru w'u Rwanda. <ref name="2R">https://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?vr=seyo&fromlat=-1.9536111&fromlng=30.0605556&tolat=-2.6911111&tolng=29.0216667&fromplace=Kigali,%20Kigali%20Rwanda%20RW&toplace=Bugarama,%20Cyangugu%20Rwanda%20RW</ref> Ruzizi IV, yegereye izindi sitasiyo eshatu z'amashanyarazi ku ruzi rwa Ruzizi, arizo Rizizi I, II na III. <ref name="1R" />

== Incamake ==
Uru rugomero rw 'amashanyarazi ni  urwa kane (4)  ku ruzi rwa Ruzizi, rugira  akamaro ibihugu [[Uburundi|by'Uburundi]], DRC n'u Rwanda. Amashanyarazi arimo Ruzizi I (29.8 megawatt) na Ruzizi II (megawatt 43.8), byombi biherereye mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bwa Ruzizi III kandi byombi byarangiye gukora guhera muri Mutarama 2020.  [[Urugomero rwa Ruzizi ya III|Sitasiyo ya Ruzizi III Amashanyarazi]] ni megawatt 147 z'amashanyarazi arimo gutezwa imbere kuva mu ntangiriro ya za 2010. <ref name="3R">https://www.hydroreview.com/2016/01/04/afdb-approves-financing-for-147-mw-ruzizi-3-hydropower-plant/</ref> Imbaraga zituruka kuri ayo mashanyarazi zisaranganywa kimwe hagati y’ibihugu bitatu bituranye. <ref name="1R" />

== Inkunga ==
Muri Mutarama 2020, [[Banki Nyafurika Itsura Amajyambere|Banki Nyafurika itsura amajyambere]] yemeje inkunga ingana na miliyoni 8 zo gutegura uyu mushinga. Ibi bikurikira bikurikira indi nkunga ya US $ 980.000 yemejwe mu mpera za 2018 ikigo gishinzwe ''ubufatanye bw’iterambere ry’ibikorwa remezo bya Afurika'' (NEPAD-IPPF), bigana ku ntego imwe.  <ref name="4R">https://www.nsenergybusiness.com/news/afdb-ruzizi-iv-hydropower/</ref>

